 <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to Stream <span>Search</span></h1>
    <header>
      <h1>Welcome to Stream Search</h1>
      <p>In todays world of endless options of sreaming services, it may seem almost impossible to orginize what
        programs are on what service. Stream Search is designed to help maximze efficency in navigating multiple 
        services.
      </p>
    </header>
      <form>
        <div class="form-group">
          <div class="preference-select">
            <p>What are your genre preferences?</p>
            <div class="pref">
              <label for="romance">Romance</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="romance" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="pref">
              <label for="action">Action</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="action" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="pref">
              <label for="drama">Drama</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="drama" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="pref">
              <label for="comedy">Comedy</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="comedy" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="pref">
              <label for="science-fiction">Science Fiction</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="science-fiction" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="pref">
              <label for="documentay">Documentary</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="documentary" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="pref">
              <label for="anime">Anime</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="Anime" checked>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="user-services">
            <p>What streaming services do you have?</p>
            <div class="service">
              <label for="netflix">Netflix</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="netflix" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
              <label for="prime">Amazon Prime</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="prime" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
              <label for="disney">Disney+</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="disney" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
              <label for="hbo">HBO Max</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="hbo" checked>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
              <label for="hulu">Hulu</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="hulu" checked>
            </div>            

            <div class="service">
              <label for="peacock">Peacock</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="peacock" checked>
            </div>            
          </div>

        <input type="text" id="inputValue">
        <button type="submit" id="search">Search a movie</button>

      </form>

    </div>

    <div id = "movie-search">
        <div class = "movie">
     </div>
    </div>

